name: CreedThoughts
0:
”Alexa, open creed thoughts”
”Alexa, ask creed thoughts about something”
”Alexa, ask creed thoughts for a thought”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: creed thoughts
des:
Hey-o, everyone out there in SyberWorld. It's old Creed Bratton coming at your again, here from my perch as a Quality Assurance Manager at Dunder Mifflin paper. Just a few observations on the world around me.
 
Ask me about something. I'll draw you a map, mama.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Creed Thoughts" or "Alexa, Ask Creed Thoughts for a thought".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
